# Backend Architecture

See [apps/server/AGENTS.md](mdc:apps/server/AGENTS.md) and [docs/architecture.md](mdc:docs/architecture.md).

## Server (Express, module-first)

- Entry: [apps/server/src/server.ts](mdc:apps/server/src/server.ts)
- App: [apps/server/src/app.ts](mdc:apps/server/src/app.ts)
- Features: [apps/server/src/modules](mdc:apps/server/src/modules)
- tRPC composition: [apps/server/src/modules/trpc/app.router.ts](mdc:apps/server/src/modules/trpc/app.router.ts)

## tRPC boundary

- Procedures: `apps/server/src/modules/<feature>/*.trpc.ts`
- Client types: [packages/trpc/src/index.ts](mdc:packages/trpc/src/index.ts) (re-export only)

## Worker / store

- Worker: [apps/worker/src/index.ts](mdc:apps/worker/src/index.ts)
- Prisma: [packages/store/prisma/schema.prisma](mdc:packages/store/prisma/schema.prisma)

## Shared backend

- Env, Redis, logging: [packages/backend-common](mdc:packages/backend-common/AGENTS.md)

## Guidelines

- Thin routes/controllers; logic in services and repositories.
- Validate at tRPC/HTTP boundaries with Zod.
- Use `@template/backend-common` for env and Redis—not raw `process.env` in app code.
